Job Qualification:
• Graduate from an accredited School of Nursing. Bachelor’s Degree in Nursing, preferred. Must be enrolled in an
accredited program within 24 months of employment, if hired after September 1, 2010 and obtain a BSN degree within
five (5) years of employment date.
• Current license to practice as a Registered Professional Nurse in New York State.
• BCLS, ACLS, preferred
